[ctccomic] "I heard that Lillium's been buying a ton of rubber ducks. That he's building an army"

Thank you to my patrons for voting on the mermay (Lillium spending hundreds to have rubber duckies express delivered to his apartment to appease the apex predator in his bathtub) prompt this month!

Characters are from Countdown to Countdown, as usual~ I feel like I have so many AUs of these two now... the CTC cinematic multiverse...
.

node.text:
(Scroll for everyone!) Ningguang, Beidou, Xinyan, and Ganyu are here! The four beauties of Liyue are now completed 🥰💖 Can you tell I’ve been hanfu shopping too much lately!??

They’re also available as art prints in my store now at velinxi.art 👀👀👀👉👈

This is like the first proper fan art I’ve done in a long while... let’s see how many months until my next 🥴 unless I decide to draw all liyue residents in hanfu
.
#genshinimpact #beidou #ningguang #xinyan #ganyu #illustration #hanfu

node.text:
My webcomic, Countdown to Countdown is back! Book 2 starts now~ You can read it with the link in my bio or at ctccomic.com 🌟

Today’s update has 4 pages! Hope you guys will enjoy chapter 5 💕

If you guys want to read 20ish pages ahead, have early access to illustrations, and see my shippy doodles and nonsense, you know where to look! (Hint: it’s my patreon)
.
#ctccomic #countdowntocountdown #hiveworks #webcomic #comics #ocs #originalcharacter

node.text:
Ganyu fan art 🌟

I'll be doing Xinyan, Beidou, and Ningguang next 👀 hanfu for everyone to fuel me✋ I haven't done proper fan art in so long and I finally am finding a bit of time and inspiration~

If anyone’s genuinely (seriously, only if you really plan on it) interested in getting prints of these girls do let me know, and maybe I’ll do a run of a set! :D
.
#ganyu #genshinimpact #illustration #hanfu
